OL,3,CJaguar Land Rover investing more than
OL,4,C#1million to target UK vehicle thefts
OL,6,FJaguar Land Rover is investing more
OL,7,Fthan one million pounds in policing to
OL,8,Ftarget vehicle thefts in the UK, as
OL,9,Fowners say their cars are proving
OL,10,Fdifficult or expensive to insure.
OL,12,FThe Coventry-based carmaker JLR says
OL,13,Fit's committing money to 'proactive
OL,14,Fpolicing' to tackle crime groups
OL,15,Ftargeting vehicles across the country.
OL,17,FThe company says the money will help
OL,18,Fpolice forces with resources to
OL,19,Frespond in car-theft hotspots.
