OL,3,CJaguar Land Rover investing more than
OL,4,C#1million to target UK vehicle thefts
OL,6,FIt will also help with increased
OL,7,Fchecks at ports which criminal gangs
OL,8,Fhave used to export vehicles.
OL,10,FIt had previously been reported that
OL,11,Fthe company's Range Rover was
OL,12,F'Britain's most stolen vehicle', but
OL,13,FAdrian Mardell, the CEO of JLR, has
OL,14,Fdescribed those claims as
OL,15,F"misinformation" and a "myth".
