OL,3,CJaguar Land Rover investing more than
OL,4,C#1million to target UK vehicle thefts
OL,6,FThe reputation has led to insurers
OL,7,Fcharging more to cover Land Rovers and
OL,8,FRange Rovers, with one driver saying
OL,9,Fhis old insurer was refusing to renew
OL,10,Fthe insurance on his Range Rover, and
OL,11,Fquotes from other insurers were more
OL,12,Fthan #10,000.
OL,14,FRaf Sabir from Birmingham says he then
OL,15,Ftried to insure directly through JLR's
OL,16,Fown insurance but was apparently
OL,17,Fdenied. He eventually found insurance
OL,18,Fbut pays more than three times his
OL,19,Fprevious annual amount.
