OL,3,CJaguar Land Rover investing more than
OL,4,C#1million to target UK vehicle thefts
OL,6,FAs well as affecting insurance costs,
OL,7,Fit's also impacted resale value, with
OL,8,FLand Rover and Range Rover models
OL,9,Fdropping more rapidly compared to the
OL,10,Fmarket average, according to figures
OL,11,Ffrom market data providers Cap Hpi.
OL,13,FJLR says its latest generation of
OL,14,Fvehicles is "highly resistant" to
OL,15,Ftheft, and that it's spent #15 million
OL,16,Fto update the security on older cars.
