OL,3,CJaguar Land Rover investing more than
OL,4,C#1million to target UK vehicle thefts
OL,6,FPatrick McGillycuddy, Managing
OL,7,FDirector JLR UK, said: "We are
OL,8,Fconstantly developing our systems and
OL,9,Fsecurity features and through our
OL,10,Fclose collaboration with police, we
OL,11,Fstay ahead of any emerging methods and
OL,12,Fquickly deploy anti-theft measures.
OL,14,FThis additional investment, coupled
OL,15,Fwith our other ongoing and proactive
OL,16,Faction, shows our commitment to
OL,17,Fsupporting the authorities in having a
OL,18,Ftangible impact on combating this
OL,19,Fissue in the UK."
